<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>Payment Reminder</title>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
		<link
			href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:ital,wght@0,300..800;1,300..800&display=swap"
			rel="stylesheet"
		/>
		<style>
			body {
				font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: #333;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 20px;
			}
			.container {
				max-width: 600px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 20px;
				background-color: #f9f9f9;
				border: 1px solid #ddd;
			}
			.header,
			.footer {
				text-align: center;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
			}
			.content {
				margin-bottom: 20px;
			}
			.footer {
				font-size: 12px;
				color: #777;
			}
			.regards {
				margin-top: 20px;
				border-radius: 5px;
				font-style: italic;
			}
			.regards p {
				margin: 0;
			}
			ul {
				padding-left: 20px;
			}
			ul li {
				margin-bottom: 10px;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="content">
				<p>Dear <%= receiverName %>,</p>

				<p>Your ordered gift card is still not active.</p>
				<p>Please finalize your payment:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Total amount: <%= totalAmount %> EUR</li>
					<li>Received amount: <%= receivedAmount ?? 0 %> EUR</li>
					<li>To pay: <%= toPay %> EUR</li>
				</ul>

				<p>Bank Details:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Account holder name: <%= BankDetails?.account_holder_name || 'N/A' %></li>
					<li>IBAN: <%= BankDetails?.iban || 'N/A' %></li>
					<li>BIC: <%= BankDetails?.bic || 'N/A' %></li>
					<li>Reference: <%= BankDetails?.reference || 'N/A' %></li>
				</ul>

				<p>
					If we do not receive your payment within the next 6 days, your order
					will be canceled. If you made a partial payment, we will refund the already
					paid amount.
				</p>

				<p>Feel free to start a new order anytime.</p>

				<p>Thank you for using our service!</p>
			</div>

			<div class="footer">
				<p>
					If you have any questions, please contact our customer service team at
					<a href="mailto:support@thai-massage.de">support@thai-massage.de</a>
				</p>
				<p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Thai-Massage.de. All rights reserved.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
